OL,6,FThe family of a woman who died while
OL,7,Fin intensive care in hospital say they
OL,8,Fhave been left deeply traumatised one
OL,9,Fyear on from her death.
OL,11,FTamara Davis was admitted to the Royal
OL,12,FSussex County Hospital with sepsis and
OL,13,Fmulti-organ failure.
OL,15,FHer family say she spent 10 hours on a
OL,16,Fbed in a corridor without monitoring
OL,17,Fequipment.
