OL,6,FTamara's sister, Miya Davis said: "I
OL,7,Fcan't describe the fear I have now of
OL,8,Fmyself or friends or family having to
OL,9,Fgo into hospital now. It's terrifying."
OL,11,FMeanwhile, the family of .
OL,13,FHe suffered a 12-hour delay in
OL,14,Ftreatment for a blood clot following
OL,15,Fheart surgery.
OL,17,FSussex Police are still investigating
OL,18,Fscores of other deaths at the hospital
OL,19,Fsince 2015.
