OL,6,FA spokesperson for University
OL,7,FHospitals Sussex NHS Foundation Trust
OL,8,Fsaid: "We have extended our
OL,9,Fcondolences, and apologies, to the
OL,10,FSims family for their loss and the
OL,11,Ftremendous upset they have suffered.
OL,13,F"The care given to Mr Sims in 2019 was
OL,14,Fnot of the standard that he and his
OL,15,Ffamily should have been able to
OL,16,Fexpect, and we are deeply sorry for
OL,17,Fthat."
