OL,6,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,7,Fraised the hospital's rating from
OL,8,Finadequate to requires improvement,
OL,9,Fbut told bosses there are problems
OL,10,Fthat need to be addressed urgently.
OL,12,FThe CQC's Neil Cox said: "Frontline
OL,13,Fstaff are doing a good job at
OL,14,Fproviding care to patients.
OL,16,F"Staff have told us that the board and
OL,17,Fexec team were seen as remote and
OL,18,Fdidn't have a full understanding of
OL,19,Fthe issues affecting surgical staff
OL,20,Falways.
