OL,3,CFamily of woman who died in hospital
OL,4,Cwaiting for care left traumatised
OL,6,F"There's still a culture of bullying
OL,7,Fdespite being recognised and that's
OL,8,Fseen in some surgical departments."
OL,10,FChief executive of University
OL,11,FHospitals Sussex NHS Foundation Trust
OL,12,FGeorge Findlay said: "What I would say
OL,13,Fto staff is thank you for all the hard
OL,14,Fwork, and what I would say to patients
OL,15,Fis, our staff are amazing.
OL,17,F"They provide the best care they can
OL,18,Fpossibly. The outstanding nature of
OL,19,Fcare, recognised by the CQC should
OL,20,Fgive confidence but we know we've got
OL,21,Fimprovements to make.
